"Attach the அச்சுப்பொறி பெறுநர் the LTSP client machine (both USB and parallel "
"துறைமுகம் அரே supported)."

#. type: Content of: <article><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#, xml-text
msgid "Configure the LTSP client with GOsa² to use a fixed IP address."
msgstr "Configure the LTSP client with GOsa² பெறுநர் use a fixed IP address."

#. type: Content of: <article><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#, xml-text
msgid ""
"Configure the printer using the web interface "
